rComments: Excellent lecturer. Teacher great information and writes good exams, but they are hard.
Not helpful at all. Inconsistent in requests for papers. Does not care about her students. Poor advice. I would recommend avoiding at all costs.

Favourite prof from my entire undergrad experience at UofT! She really cares about the students. Made this course fun with fit breaks and lots of examples, even a meditation class. Fair marker for all exams, helps you prep for them and gives lots of great advice for study tips. Loved the stress and coping class!!
